The invention relates to a raw wheat koji fermentation system and a raw wheat koji fermentation method. The raw wheat koji fermentation system comprises a fermentation room, wherein an air inlet pipe is connected to one side of the fermentation room; a control box is connected to one end of the air inlet pipe; suspended ceiling fixing parts are arranged at the top of the fermentation room; one-side steel plate partition walls are arranged on two sides of the fermentation room; folded part connecting strips are mounted between the suspended ceiling fixing parts; one ends of the one-side steel plate partition walls are connected with the folded part connecting strips, and the other ends of the one-side steel plate partition walls are connected with earthen walls; electrical lifting doors are mounted on the front and rear sides of the fermentation room; cold-hot air pipes are laid at the bottom of the fermentation room; and a plurality of round holes are formed in each cold-hot air pipe; two parallel tracks are mounted at the bottom of the fermentation room and are positioned above the cold-hot air pipes. According to the system, the temperature in a wheat fermentation process can be accurately controlled through the control box and cannot be influenced by season, and the quality of raw wheat koji is very stable; the raw wheat koji is output from the electrical lifting door through the tracks after the fermentation is finished, and the whole process is automated, so that the labor cost is reduced and the labor efficiency is improved.
